These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, frog, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | cat | lizard | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, july, october
1. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | july | december | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, juice, coffee
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee | cola | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, fonseca, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##7
2. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
3. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | ritmeester | fonseca | prince |

